<p class="ayah 40-10" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieved</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُنَادَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be cried out to them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمَقْتُ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Certainly Allah`s hatred</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْبَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) greater</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّقْتِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your hatred</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنفُسَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) yourselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُدْعَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you were called</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</sp