<p class="ayah 40-11" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They (will) say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Our Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَتَّنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You gave us death</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱثْنَتَيْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">twice</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَحْيَيْتَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and You gave us life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱثْنَتَيْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">twice,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱعْتَرَفْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and we confess</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِذُنُوبِنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our sins.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَهَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So is (there)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خُرُوجٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">get out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span